Product description

Top quality tail pipe muffler

We’ve sourced the best stainless steel to produce our muffler tips which features extremely strong anti-corrosive properties as well as good corrosion resistance to alkali solutions, most organic and inorganic acids too.

Car tail pipe features

Each of our stainless steel, chrome looking muffler tips features a small drainage hole on the bottom end of the tip to prevent water build-up.

Easy for any skill level to install

Whether you love working on cars or you literally have no idea when it comes to car mechanics, it doesn’t matter because our tail muffler is super easy to install. Unlike other tips on the market, ours doesn’t need any drilling or welding to install. You can install it quickly and easily on your own driveway with just 3 clamps which are included with your purchase. Never before has it been so easy to add finishing touches to your automobile.

A great gift

Treat a car enthusiast or someone who just wants the sweetest ride in town to our muffler exhaust tip. It makes an affordable but thoughtful gift and is makes an ideal Birthday gift for a car lover as well as a great gift for Christmas, Valentine’s Day, Father’s Day and more!

BUY NOW and don’t settle for factory standard, give your car some cool finishing touches so it looks the best in town
